show:
toggle visibility of section (short word).

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-hide}}
{{Identical|Show}}

hide:
toggle visibility of section (short word).

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-show}}
{{Identical|Hide}}

deleted:
Used as header for the column containing number of deleted pages.

Also used to indicate preceding pagename has already been deleted like "Pagename1 (Deleted)".
{{Identical|Deleted}}

others:
label in chart for the rest.

Preceded by an integer. e.g. "67 others"
{{Identical|Other}}

months:
time months.

Used as header for the column containing months. e.g. "2013 / 1"
{{Identical|Month}}

start:
menu option to limit the search.

Also used as label for "time and date" field.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-end}}
{{identical|Start date}}

end:
menu option to limit the search.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-start}}
{{Identical|End date}}

live:
Live edits, visible edits of a user.

(Live edits) = (Total edits) - (Deleted edits)

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-total}}
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-deleted edits}}

avg_timebwedits_sign:
label with Ø-sign, the average time between two edits.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-timebwedits|tooltip}}

minor:
edits marked as minor.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-major}}
{{Identical|Minor edit}}

major:
normal edits, no minor edits.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-minor}}

events:
Events that have a log entry.

Used as header for the column containing events e.g. "modify: 2 · move: 1 · move_prot: 1"
{{Identical|Event}}

support:
exact term for support on vote pages, aka the [[File:Symbol support vote.svg|15px|link=]] '''Support'''.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-neutral}}
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-oppose}}
{{Identical|Support}}

oppose:
exact term for oppose on vote pages, aka the [[File:Symbol oppose vote.svg|15px|link=]] '''Oppose'''.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-neutral}}
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-support}}
{{Identical|Oppose}}

neutral:
exact term for neutral on vote pages, aka the [[File:Symbol neutral vote.svg|15px|link=]] '''Neutral'''.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-oppose}}
* {{msg-intuition|X'stools-support}}
{{Identical|Neutral}}
